finnmath.util

Class MathRandom

  • Object
    • MathRandom

  • @Beta
public final class MathRandom
extends Object
    A pseudo random generator for long, BigDecimal, Fraction, SimpleComplexNumber, RealComplexNumber, BigIntVector, DecimalVector, BigIntMatrix and DecimalMatrix
    Since:
    1
